都是你安放情绪的方式，为你所用。
It's the way you put your emotions, for you to use.
是华丽词藻，是平铺直叙，都没关系，只要文字能够表达你的心意。
Is gorgeous rhetoric, is flat, all right, as long as the words can express your mind.
拿笔记下这段“隔离”，是为了以后和这座城走得更紧。
Take notes under this section of "isolation", so that later and the city to go closer.
《"爸，我还回家过年吗？"》来源：公众号微湖美书法总有一种魔力，可以在寥寥数笔之间，述尽衷肠。
A: Dad, did I ever go home for the New Year? S: Public Name Microlake Calligraphy has a magic touch that can be expressed in just a few strokes.
笔迹，也因倾注的心力不同，各有特点。
The handwriting, also due to the pouring of different heart power, each has its own characteristics.
提笔写下你对武汉的祝福，鼓励，又或者只是一段简单的记录，让你对这座城市的情感来主导笔画的走向。
Write down your wish to Wuhan, encourage, or just a simple record of your feelings about the city to guide the direction of the painting.
“共克时艰”“武汉加油”“平安”……绞转与提按间，完成和这座城市的切切私语。
"Together difficult times", "Wuhan refueling", "peace...... twist and lift between, and the completion of this city's whispers.
湖北美术馆艺术总监艺术家傅中望先生为疫情所写合美术馆执行馆长鲁虹在疫情期间书写武汉美术馆张文博在疫情期间所写孩子或许不能像大人一样，在一次疫情中看到人性、看清现实。
Mr. Fu Zhongwang, artistic director of Hubei Art Museum, wrote about the outbreak by Lu Hongbo, executive director of the gallery. During the outbreak, Zhang Wenbo, an art gallery in Wuhan, wrote that children may not be able to see humanity and reality in an epidemic, as adults do.
但他们知道，自然可敬生命可畏。
But they know that nature is awesome.
一支画笔和一张画纸构成的表达，有无限种。
An expression consisting of a brush and a piece of paper having an infinite variety.
作者：黄玺月 6岁视心弦美术工作室提供作者：彭小淼 11岁视心弦美术工作室提供作者：付恺祎 12岁视心弦美术工作室提供... ...除上述列举的形式以外，如由其他形式作品，也欢迎投稿。
Author: Peng Xiaomiao 11-year-old visual chord art studio provides: Fu Yi Yi 12-year-old visual chord art studio to provide... in addition to the above-mentioned forms, other forms of works also welcome contributions.
我们不会隔离任何一种表达。
We don't isolate any expression.
